item.description:
@jkicool wrote:

If you wan to change the Ip in your client you will need to follow these step’s:
1.Go open client.java with what ever editing software(default notepad)
2.Search “server” (without parenthesis)
3.Change it to what Ip address you wan’t
4.Compile
5.Your are Done.
